build
=====

smoke test, build system, overview pages

master
------

requirements:
- osc command line tool for OBS and a project with packages on it
- web server to host the puglished overview and log info pages

coordinator
-----------

requirements:
- virtualization software, currently only VirtualBox is supported
- wget and ftp client

builder
-------

requirements:
- cron (for @reboot)
- git (to check out software)
- wget and ftp client
